criticalIssues.recommendation:
Move self._last_flow_time = time.monotonic() to BEFORE the is_target_domain() guard. The request() hook is called for every flow; the timestamp must be recorded for all of them, not just target-domain ones:

  def request(self, flow: http.HTTPFlow) -> None:
      self._last_flow_time = time.monotonic()   # track ALL traffic
      if not is_target_domain(flow.request.host):
          return
      ...
